WEBVTT

00:02:29.995 --> 00:02:31.860
give your heart, give your spirit.

00:02:33.090 --> 00:02:35.033
The world will say to you,

00:02:36.516 --> 00:02:38.808
"We need peace."

00:02:39.904 --> 00:02:41.737
Find your peace within,

00:02:42.304 --> 00:02:43.998
hold it sacred,

00:02:44.022 --> 00:02:46.659
bring it with you everywhere you go.

00:02:47.029 --> 00:02:50.989
Peace cannot be shared
or created with others

00:02:51.013 --> 00:02:53.589
if we cannot first generate it within.

00:02:54.218 --> 00:02:55.830
The world will say to you,

00:02:55.854 --> 00:02:57.619
"They are the enemy."

00:02:58.357 --> 00:02:59.700
Love enough to know

00:02:59.724 --> 00:03:02.733
that just because someone
disagrees with you,